Sentencas: Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-delta (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) were synthesized by a modified complexing sol-gel process as cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The phase structure, thermodynamic properties and electrochemical properties of the materials were characterized by X-ray diffraction, thermal expansion coefficient test, conductivity test, polarization impedance (R) test and single cell performance test.
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results showed that all samples were successfully synthesized with perovskite-like structure.
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-delta cathode exhibited good chemical compatibility with the Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 (SDC) electrolyte at 1 000 degrees C for 5 h.
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The coefficient of thermal expansion (TEC) decreased with the increase of x, and the minimum value was 1.839x10(-5) K-1.
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Its high temperature conductivity increased with the increase of Ni doping content, and SEN30 had the highest conductivity of 101 S.cm(-1).
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The R-p of this series of samples showed a trend of decrease first and then increase with the increase of the doping content of Ni. SEN10 had the lowest polarization impedance of 0.078 8 Omega.cm(2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The trend of the output power of the electrolyte-supported cell was consistent with the trend of polarization impedance.
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The SEN10 achieved an output power density of 421.6 mW.cm(-2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and Performance of Sr3Fe2-xNixO7-δ (x=0, 0.1, 0.2, 0.3) Cathode for Intermediate-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
